dialogue.text: Who the funk is that guy?
Oh, Speedy! That's an outcase. He came from outside the comic.
You mean fan character that isn't canan to the comic but makes fan content for the comic? Like TheAutistic1 or Seth the Lucario?
Oh, I don't know. He doesn't look like us. He must be some kinda demension traveler or something.
Oh right! Hey speedy, you should rap battle this guy. He's really good at it.
Oh alright. I ain't gonna go easy on him though. I may have had brain damage but I can still sing fast.
